<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF109-618-855  </DOCNO><DOCID>09 618 855.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>EDGE: Work-Group Computing Report  Nov 5 1990 v1 n24 p19(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT EDGE Publishing 1990.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Notebook computing: Everex unveils powerful notebook computer.andO;(Everex Systems' Everex Tempo LX) (product announcement)andM;</TITLE><DESCRIPT>Company:   Everex Systems Inc. (Product introduction).andO;Ticker:    EVRX.andO;Product:   Everex Systems Tempo LX (Portable computer) (Productintroduction).andO;Topic:     Product IntroductionMicrocomputersHardware VendorsNotebook Computers.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>Everex Systems Inc. Monday announced the Everex Tempo LX, a full-featured386SX-based notebook computer with a retail price of $3,899.andM;Offering all of the power and capabilities of heavier 386SX-based laptopcomputers, the Tempo LX weighs 6.9 pounds with battery and fits into astandard-size briefcase.andM;Measuring 2 inches by 10 inches by 12 inches, the Tempo LX is small enough tocarry comfortably while traveling and includes a padded, nylon carrying caseto hold both the system and its accessories.andM;&quot;Currently, 386SX-based laptops often weigh over fifteen pounds, leavingusers wodering about the definition of portable.andP;  The Tempo LX will changethe public's standards for portability and power,&quot; said Dennis Jow, productchampion.andM;The Tempo LX is powered by a rechargeable NiCAD battery and featuresautomatic and manual power management controls to extend battery charge.andM;The Tempo LX will also run off AC power through the universal voltage ACadapter/recharger included with the system.andP;  In recharging mode, the adapteris capable of fully recharging a completely discharged battery in less thanan hour, the fastest recharge time available on any laptop.andM;Equipped with a twisted backlit CFL liquid crystal display, the Tempo LXfetures a non-glare VGA screen designed to reduce eye strain and enhancevisibility in adverse lighting.andM;In addition to the Tempo LX, Everex Systems also manufactures a complete lineof Tempo desktop personal computers.andP;  Offering quality systems at affordableprices, the Tempo line includes the Tempo 286/12, Tempo 286/16, Tempo386SX/16, Tempo 386/20 and Tempo 386/25.andO;</TEXT></DOC>